I've been into RSPS since 2007 and i have collected a lot of stuff since then, i decided it is best to release all my config related items, sorry no crashers :P.
Here is a list:
Z O D I A C's list Interface Dumps Some Frames Emotes Co ords Ultimate Config pack 100% Rs Npcs & AutoSpawn Delta's Items 30% Shops [b]-------------> AMAZING FREE 100% DECOMPILER!!!! <-----------[/b] Voule Tools Shop Maker
